summary:
Teamleader with substantial experience in both the Dutch High School environment, and the volunteer driven World Bank Family Network in a multicultural environment. Strong knowledge of all aspects of management, liaising with multiple partners,  motivation of team members. Focus on refinement and development of new programs as suited for changing membership.

Specialties: Skills: Interpersonal/Intercultural Understanding, Oral & Written Communication in Dutch, French, English; Organization & Program Development; Curriculum Design;Newsletter Management; Teaching & Tutoring;Event Planning; and, Computer skills

Languages: Fluent in Dutch (native), French , English
Proficient in German, Spanish; 

Global Experience: Lived in Indonesia, Cameroun, Netherlands, Belgium, USA
Traveled extensively through China, India, Indonesia, Europe, South-America, and USA
